[h1]Faction - Elves - Modernized[/h1]

Combat Extended compatibility and combat overhaul for [url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3726293423]Faction - Elves[/url] by ICC.

Elves carry rifles now. They still care deeply about how they do it.

[b]Requires:[/b] [url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2890901044]Combat Extended[/url] + [url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3726293423]Faction - Elves[/url]

Each elven faction gets a proper CE loadout: magazines, shields, sidearms, and ammo weights. The goal was to give every pawn kind a clear combat role without turning elves into generic gun guys. Wild Elves are untouched. Celestia was already spacer-tier and just needed the plumbing.

[hr][/hr]

[h2]🏹 High Elvish Kingdom[/h2]
[list]
[*][b]Scout[/b] - M16A4, light armor, FMJ. Skirmisher.
[*][b]Ranger[/b] - Assault rifle or DMR, medium armor. Line infantry.
[*][b]Sharpshooter[/b] - Precision rifle, HP/AP/IncAP ammo. Stays back.
[*][b]Warden[/b] - Smoke launcher and pistol, energy shield. Covers the advance.
[*][b]Swordmaster[/b] - Elite melee with a sidearm for insurance.
[*][b]Emperor[/b] - Precision rifle, melee, ballistic shield. The one you don't want to see.
[/list]

[h2]🗡️ Dark Elvish Kingdom[/h2]
[list]
[*][b]Scout[/b] - SMG with a forced melee sidearm. Gets in close.
[*][b]Reaver[/b] - SMG and shotgun, devilstrand hood, no helmet. New pawn kind.
[*][b]Marauder[/b] - One-handed melee behind a ballistic shield. Smoke grenades to close the gap.
[*][b]Blademaster[/b] - Elite melee with a sidearm and a shield.
[*][b]Spearmen[/b] - Polearm, shield, smoke. Unchanged role.
[*][b]Lord[/b] - Precision rifle and melee. Faction leader.
[/list]

[h2]🌲 Wild Elvish Tribe[/h2]
[list]
[*]No changes to combat roles. Bows, spears, tribal shields, arrow magazines. That's it.
[/list]

[h2]✨ Celestia Elvish Empire[/h2]
[list]
[*]Spacer gear was already there. This just wires up magazines, shields, and sidearms properly.
[*]Councilor, BladeMaster, Ranger, and Mechanitor all configured.
[/list]

[hr][/hr]

[h2]🔧 Custom tags[/h2]
[list]
[*][b]ElvesExpanded_Shotgun[/b] - Added to all 12-gauge weapons. Reavers use this instead of CE_AI_BROOM so they don't spawn with handguns.
[*][b]ElvesExpanded_AssaultRifle[/b] - Added to the vanilla M16A4 only. Keeps the scout pool clean.
[*][b]ElvesExpanded_40mmSmokeLauncher[/b] - Added to all 40x46mm launchers. Used by the warden.
[/list]

[h2]⚙️ CE loadout features[/h2]
[list]
[*]LoadoutPropertiesExtension on every combat pawn kind
[*]Ballistic and energy shields with budget-driven variety
[*]Forced sidearms and magazine counts per role
[*]Weighted ammo: FMJ, AP, HP, incendiary, smoke
[*]Smoke grenades for melee units that need to close distance
[/list]

[h2]📊 Tech level changes[/h2]
[list]
[*]High Elvish Kingdom: Medieval → Industrial
[*]Dark Elvish Kingdom: Medieval → Industrial
[*]Wild Elvish Tribe: unchanged
[*]Celestia Elvish Empire: unchanged
[/list]

